'''Occasional furniture''' refers to small pieces of [[furniture]] that can be put to varied uses as the occasion demands.<ref>[http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/occasional Merriam-Webster on line dictionary]</ref> Items such as small [[Table (furniture)|tables]], [[nightstand]]s, [[Chest (furniture)|chests]], [[commode]]s, and easily moved [[chair]]s are usually included in this category.
